This program performs basic arithmetic operations (addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division) on two integers inputted by the user. It provides an easy-to-use interface for performing these calculations and handles division by zero gracefully.

Features
Addition: Computes the sum of two integers.
Subtraction: Computes the difference between two integers.
Multiplication: Computes the product of two integers.
Division: Computes the quotient of two integers, with handling for division by zero.
Formatted Output: The division result is displayed with two decimalÂ precision.
